        <p>
            <strong>Key challenge</strong><br>
            Customer value is still low - how do we improve this without adding new features?
        </p>
        <p>
            <strong>Approach</strong><br>
            Push to make filling out the portal a more pleasurable experience. 
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc mb-8 ml-10">
            <li>Worked with Art Director to help inform new visual direction for JCT600 and create a wider (and accessible) colour palette to work from, and allow us to bring in slicker design elements and illustrations</li>
            <li>Redesigned all elements and put the foundations of a design system in place to allow for easier iteration and growth in the future</li>
            <li>Started designing animations and micro-interactions both to create a more enjoyable experience, but also to to provide reassurance in tasks that involve submitting user information</li>
        </ul>
